        </p>
        <p><bdi>&lt;bdi&gt; indicates </bdi> a different text-flow direction.</p>
        <p><bdo>&lt;bdo&gt; indicates </bdo>an override for text-flow direction.</p>
        <p>the<br>&lt;br&gt; tag is used to create a line break.</p>
