            </ruby>
            <rp>(</rp><rt>mirai dot audio</rt><rp>)</rp>
          </ruby>
          to help with pronunciation.
          {{t "app.styleguide.lorem-ipsum-en"}}
        </p>
        <p><s>This text has a strikethrough</s>.</p>
        <p>
          <strong>Sample &lt;samp&gt; output:</strong>
          <samp>This is sample output from a computer program.</samp>
        </p>
        <p><small>This small text is small for for fine print, etc.</small></p>
        <p>
          The HTML &lt;span&gt; element is a generic inline container for
          phrasing content, which does not inherently represent anything.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Strong is used to indicate strong importance.</strong></p>
        <p>Lastly don't forget the sub (H<sub>2</sub>O)</p>
        <p>Superscript<sup>®</sup>.</p>
        <p>
          The time element:
          <time datetime="2013-04-06T12:32+00:00">2 weeks ago</time>
        </p>
        <p>
